-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-17/switzerland-s-franc-strengthens-versus-euro-dollar-reversing-decline.html
The Swiss franc extended gains
against the euro and the dollar after the nation’s central bank
said it will take further measures if needed to combat the
currency’s strength.  To contact the reporter on this story:
